      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAKEVIEW SNEAKY (1) filled the minor money two on end before breaking through for a deserved win last time, scoring at this track over 425m (24.31). Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Looks to have an edge on most of these. MOMENT (2) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at Sale in a handy 29.17 beating Be A Shadow. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Can make it back-to-back wins. HE SHINES (8) lines up for the first time at this track. Failed to feature at Warragul behind Point Break last start over 460m (26.22) in Grade 4/5. In the mix.",
